Core Data

tsg_core_data.Rd

Given a list returned by [tsg_all_grants()] or [tsg_search_grants()], creates a tibble with the core variables required by the [360Giving](https://standard.threesixtygiving.org/en/latest/) open standard, as well as the publisher prefix, which is useful for data processing, and the licence the data was published under.

tsg_core_data(x, verbose = TRUE)

Arguments

x

A list of tibble with grant data returned by [tsg_all_grants()].
verbose

If `TRUE`, prints console messages.

Value

A tibble with core variables

Examples

# \donttest{
grants <- tsg_all_grants()
